{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6e972488-6644-4ffa-8f75-f3f7cdb5eb7b",
    "name": "One Million Copy - Leads API",
    "description": "# Instrucciones de uso\n\nEsta coleccion contiene las APIs del backend de leads.\n\n## 1) Levantar el proyecto\n\nOpcion local:\n- npm install\n- npm run prisma:generate\n- npm run prisma:migrate:deploy\n- npm run prisma:seed\n- npm run start:dev\n\nOpcion Docker:\n- npm run docker:up\n- docker compose exec api npm run prisma:migrate:deploy\n- docker compose exec api npm run prisma:seed\n\n## 2) Variables de la coleccion\n\n- hostUrl: URL host de la API\n- baseUrl: URL base con prefijo /api\n- docsUrl: URL de Swagger\n- apiKey: header x-api-key\n- leadId: se llena automaticamente al crear un lead\n\n## 3) Flujo recomendado\n\n1. Health check\n2. Crear lead\n3. Listar leads\n4. Obtener lead por ID\n5. Actualizar lead\n6. Estadisticas\n7. Resumen IA\n8. Webhook\n9. Eliminar lead\n\n## 4) Notas\n\n- Los endpoints de /leads usan API key por header x-api-key.\n- /health no requiere auth, pero puede recibir el header sin problema.\n- Si no hay key de LLM configurada, /leads/ai/summary devuelve resumen mock.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "apikey",
    "apikey": [
      {
        "key": "key",
        "value": "x-api-key",
        "type": "string"
      },
      {
        "key": "value",
        "value": "{{apiKey}}",
        "type": "string"
      },
      {
        "key": "in",
        "value": "header",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Guia",
      "description": "Carpeta de onboarding rapido para la coleccion.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Swagger UI",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Abre la documentacion Swagger para inspeccionar modelos y respuestas.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docsUrl}}",
              "host": [
                "{{docsUrl}}"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "01 - Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Verifica que la API esta arriba.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "health"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Leads CRUD",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create lead",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('leadId', data.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Crea un nuevo lead. Guarda id en la variable leadId para requests siguientes.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Postman Lead\",\n  \"email\": \"postman.lead.{{$timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"telefono\": \"+573001234567\",\n  \"fuente\": \"instagram\",\n  \"producto_interes\": \"Curso de copywriting\",\n  \"presupuesto\": 450\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/leads",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "leads"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List leads",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
